{"tid":631072,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大學生爭辯比賽 主題美斯C.朗拿度人品:個矮敢踢球很輕狂","createTime":"2018-04-16T06:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T11:18:33.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f1198c83515f3b70abe4286fdd7f79fe6fb5061","tid":631072,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:43:51.000Z","msg":"2018年04月16日11:38<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/04/16/c/c6b187b85d885308ebe76a5770fefb48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2Fc%2Fc6b187b85d885308ebe76a5770fefb48.jpg&h=127c1afb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對美斯球場上的表現有不同的評價，但在所有人看來，美斯是謙遜低調的代表，他只專注於踢球，場外除了家庭也沒有其他的愛好。<br />\n<br />\n　　不過卻有人就美斯的人品展開了辯論。在「華語辯論世界盃」上，來自兩所高校的代表就「美斯是否輕狂」這個話題展開了激烈的辯論。<br />\n<br />\n　　這場辯論的議題是「人不輕狂枉/亦少年」，在辯論過程中，美斯被當做論據提了出來，於是就有了正反雙方關於「美斯是否輕狂」的議論。<br />\n<br />\n　　來自中國重慶大學的代表站在反方的角度（人不輕狂亦少年），表示美斯是內斂、謙虛的代表。而新加坡國立大學的正方代表說：「美斯身材那麼矮，大家都不看好他，一個小個子，敢去踢球，難道還不輕狂嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/04/16/2/22c2f2f3eff4e333105caa622591026b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2F2%2F22c2f2f3eff4e333105caa622591026b.jpg&h=dd222b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/04/16/e/e3e3021042bf87b6605500999cec1533.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2Fe%2Fe3e3021042bf87b6605500999cec1533.jpg&h=9dc09964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而反方則反駁說美斯這可以說是有勇氣，但不是輕狂。他還說到：「所有看足球的人都知道，C.朗拿度是輕狂的代表，美斯是不輕狂的代表。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/04/16/2/2fee55e791b17494cdb87488b478c0fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2F2%2F2fee55e791b17494cdb87488b478c0fa.jpg&h=9f538c0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而評委則表示，說美斯是一個輕狂的人，這還挺難接受的。</span><br />\n<br />\n　　【注】輕狂：指非常輕浮、狂妄。"},{"pid":"a60d07cb650693d45e58bc2e5f064d3701d475a1","tid":631072,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:45:16.000Z","msg":"丙朗呢"},{"pid":"cf332fa21efe8acc500296b72a1b105c64ed5c78","tid":631072,"uid":35176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:47:08.000Z","msg":"反美果然弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f14e72bdcfc341144296c4bd46caa204b10f49b","tid":631072,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf332fa21efe8acc500296b72a1b105c64ed5c78","tid":631072,"uid":35176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:47:08.000Z","msg":"反美果然弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a83f17f4d872e2e8470629e75a6bd765929929","tid":631072,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:49:12.000Z","msg":"鳴辯盃 雲格退休對阿仙奴利大於弊"},{"pid":"86e5b19efe91c87cef1a921a6c5599d68811493e","tid":631072,"uid":72621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16a83f17f4d872e2e8470629e75a6bd765929929","tid":631072,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:49:12.000Z","msg":"鳴辯盃 雲格退休對阿仙奴利大於弊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:53:29.000Z","msg":"無人證明到換左一定好過唔換<br />\n所以要永續<br />\n無左雲加就會好似無左廢蛇既獌咁跌到第7<br />\n你想唔想?"},{"pid":"07c177453f9f413128389c348bc0e59f971aeca1","tid":631072,"ui